rows.label: tlk45320159_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Not much to see past here.
It's all wasteland and power plants.

rows.label: tlk45320159_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You'll want to watch out for
monsters, though.

rows.label: tlk45320159_01_msg0003
rows.name:
We fend off the monsters out there
to stop them getting into the city.
They're no walk in the park.

rows.label: tlk45320159_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Even with our advanced Superbian
steam rifles, they don't go down easily.
